sub_title: Judge, Kosovo Specialist Chambers / Reserve International Co-Prosecutor at the Extraordinary Chambers in the Courts of Cambodia
summary:
Judge of the Kosovo Specialist Chambers in The Hague,  the Reserve International Co-Prosecutor at the Extraordinary Chambers in the Courts of Cambodia, and an associate tenant at Doughty Street Chambers.
Trained and qualified as a lawyer at Freshfields Bruckhaus Deringer, and  admitted to the Bar of Ireland. Speaks and reads Spanish and French, and reads Italian and Portuguese.
